Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:02.77,CN-SUB uta,,0,0,0,,思君终不见…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:04.64,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,同时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:06.42,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,但是牌在己阵 算我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:07.24,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:09.84,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,我抢到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:10.71,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:12.48,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,是我比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:14.08,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:15.55,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,但是 刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:15.55,CN-SUB T,,0,0,0,,惠梦她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:18.08,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,我比你快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:19.35,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,跟人争牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.57,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,小夕 不要说我是白痴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:25.00,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,是我把大家带进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:27.46,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,我想让大家高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:29.91,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,要挑战女王的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:31.77,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:34.33,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,虽然争不过你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:36.84,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,那就算还你刚才的那个人情了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:41.08,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,没事的 绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:43.71,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,做回平时的你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:48.08,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:51.17,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,现在开始进攻 瑞泽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.15,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:53.82,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,好了 再拿一张…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:54.40,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,再拿一张！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:55.75,CN-SUB,,0,0,0,,一定要拿下一张
